{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加深对电压表构造的理解，学会把电流表改装成电压表的方法。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">串联电路有分压作用。</span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电源、开关、电压表、电流表、定值电阻、滑动变阻器、小灯泡</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.将灵敏电流计与定值电阻串联后接入电路；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.闭合开关</span>S<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察灵敏电流计示数与电压表示数。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">给电流表串联一定阻值的电阻可以把电流表改装成一定量程的电压表。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改装后量程与串联电阻关系：</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>U=I</em>(<em>R+r</em>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}